OL,3,CWitnesses told 'consider your
OL,4,Cconsciences' after mum shot dead
OL,6,FPolice investigating the murder of a
OL,7,Fyoung mother in Sheffield have told
OL,8,Fwitnesses to "consider their own
OL,9,Fconsciences".
OL,11,FShanice Brookes, a 30-year-old mother
OL,12,Fof one, died after she was shot
OL,13,Foutside the One Four One bar on West
OL,14,FStreet in the early hours of Bank
OL,15,FHoliday Monday.
OL,17,FDetectives say she was an innocent
OL,18,Fbystander caught in crossfire
OL,19,Ffollowing an earlier altercation.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
