OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1781007071
OL,3,CWitnesses told 'consider your
OL,4,Cconsciences' after mum shot dead
OL,6,FTwo people have been charged in
OL,7,Fconnection with Shanice's murder, but
OL,8,FSouth Yorkshire Police said key
OL,9,Fwitnesses have not yet come forward.
OL,11,FThe force has issued a series of
OL,12,Fimages of people they want to find.
OL,14,FDet Insp Matt Bolger said: "We know
OL,15,Fthere were people in the area who saw
OL,16,Fwhat happened before and after the
OL,17,Fshooting. Yet despite our appeal,
OL,18,Fnobody has come forward to tell us
OL,19,Fwhat they saw."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1781007071
OL,3,CWitnesses told 'consider your
OL,4,Cconsciences' after mum shot dead
OL,6,FHe added: "These people are not
OL,7,Fsuspects. They are witnesses -
OL,8,Fwitnesses who may hold information
OL,9,Fthat could help us deliver justice.
OL,11,F"I am asking each of them, and anyone
OL,12,Fwho recognises them, to consider their
OL,13,Fown conscience and remember that a
OL,14,Fchild has been robbed of his mum. A
OL,15,Ffamily is living every day with a
OL,16,Fgrief they did not deserve."
OL,18,FThe detective also warned anyone
OL,19,Fhiding the murder weapon they would
OL,20,Fface the "full force of the law".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1781007071
OL,3,CWitnesses told 'consider your
OL,4,Cconsciences' after mum shot dead
OL,6,F"If you have been forced to hold this
OL,7,Fweapon, or you are in fear, you can
OL,8,Fcontact us in confidence," he said.
OL,9,F"We will protect you.
OL,11,F"However, let me be absolutely clear -
OL,12,Fif we find you hiding this gun, you
OL,13,Fwill face the full force of the law.
OL,14,FYou will regret choosing to protect a
OL,15,Fweapon that has killed a young mother.
OL,16,FThis is bigger than criminal rivalries
OL,17,For loyalties. A young mother is dead.
OL,18,FA child has no mother because of this
OL,19,Fgun."
OL,26,@sD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
