CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1781007071
OL,3,CWitnesses told 'consider your
OL,4,Cconsciences' after mum shot dead
OL,6,FJemele Rhone, 30, of Outram Road, has
OL,7,Fbeen charged with Shanice's murder.
OL,9,FDeiryen Dyce, of Ellesmere Road North,
OL,10,FSheffield, is charged with assisting
OL,11,Fan offender along with drugs and
OL,12,Fweapons offences.
OL,14,FA trial date for both defendants has
OL,15,Fbeen provisionally set for 4 January
OL,16,Fnext year, with a further hearing
OL,17,Fscheduled set for 13 July.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
